---
import { siteData } from '../data/site.ts';
---

<section id="solucoes" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-neutral-light">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-primary-blue/10 text-primary-blue font-semibold rounded-full text-sm mb-4">
            Aumente sua visibilidade orgânica
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-6 leading-tight">
            Coloque cada atração do seu empreendimento no Google Maps.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-4">Atualmente, no Google Maps:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-base">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-2 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                <span>Seu parque aparece como um único marcador (pin)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-2 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                <span>As atrações internas estão invisíveis para quem pesquisa</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-2 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                <span>Não aparecem no Street View</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                
                <span>Você esta perdendo visibilidade <b>orgânica</b> e oportunidades de consumo todos os dias.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-4">A Solução: Geolocalização Estratégica</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 text-base">
              Estruturamos e posicionamos cada atração interna do empreendimento no Google Maps, gerando mais visualizações, interações e visitas.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-base">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 bg-primary-green rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span>Cada atração passa a ter presença própria no Google Maps</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 bg-primary-green rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span>Turistas encontram experiências específicas ao pesquisar no Google</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 bg-primary-green rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span> Mais visibilidade orgânica, engajamento e oportunidades de consumo dentro do parque</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Action Buttons -->
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a 
            href="#contato"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-primary-blue hover:bg-primary-darkblue text-white font-bold rounded-2xl transition-all duration-200 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 text-center"
          >
            Solicitar análise gratuita
            <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          
          <a 
            href="#clientes"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-transparent border-2 border-primary-blue text-primary-blue hover:bg-primary-blue hover:text-white font-semibold rounded-2xl transition-all duration-200 text-center"
          >
            Ver Prova Real
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image/Visual -->
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Main Image Container -->
          <div class="relative rounded-3xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden bg-neutral-dark/10 border-4 border-white">
            <img
              src="/images/banner-carrosssel/mapa-interativo.jpg"
              alt="Geolocalização estratégica no Google Maps"
              class="w-full h-[520px] sm:h-[560px] lg:h-[620px] object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-neutral-dark/60 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>

            <div class="absolute left-6 right-6 bottom-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
              <div class="bg-white/95 backdrop-blur rounded-2xl p-5 border border-white shadow-xl transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-blue/10 text-primary-blue rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path></svg>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-xs text-primary-blue font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">DESCOBERTA ORGÂNICA</p>
                </div>
                <p class="text-base font-bold text-neutral-dark">Suas atrações visíveis no Google</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Cada ponto do seu parque vira uma nova porta de entrada para quem pesquisa na região.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="bg-white/95 backdrop-blur rounded-2xl p-5 border border-white shadow-xl transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform hidden sm:block">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-green/10 text-primary-green rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-xs text-primary-green font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">ANÁLISE DE GAPS</p>
                </div>
                <p class="text-base font-bold text-neutral-dark">Pontos que hoje são invisíveis</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Identificamos atrações que não geram visitas por falta de presença correta no mapa.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Floating UI Elements -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 bg-white rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-2xl border border-gray-100 flex items-center gap-4 animate-bounce-slow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-blue text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl shadow-lg">
              📍
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark">+ Visibilidade</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Orgânica no Maps</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes bounce-slow {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(-5%);
      animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.8, 0, 1, 1);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(0);
      animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }
  }
  .animate-bounce-slow {
    animation: bounce-slow 3s infinite;
  }
</style>
